sources.description:
7th Secret - Wealth, beauty, love...the young wife of a powerful attorney seems to have it all until a mysterious man offers her a life of forbidden pleasures. Guided by the mistresses of his secret club, she must choose to either resist and run or give in to her submissive side to fulfil her wildest fantasies and risk her perfect life. What happens when we give into our secret desires?
2022.  Stars: Amanda Figueroa, Lukas Hassel, Michael Patrick Lane, Natasha Henstridge, Stacey Dash
